# Adding new org (spiderman) to the network

## Step 1: Edit the crypto-config.yaml file

Edit the file to add the new org

## Step 2: Extend the crypto materials using cryptogen

`cryptogen extend --config ./config-files/crypto-config.yaml`

## Step3: Edit the docker compose files

## Step4: generate the config materials for the spiderman org, input for this file is configtx.yaml it can be a separate file from the genesis file
`configtxgen -printOrg SpidermanMSP > ../spiderman.json`

Follow below link steps

https://hyperledger-fabric.readthedocs.io/en/release-2.2/channel_update_tutorial.html
